dex","keywords":["postprocessor","css","postcss","pleeease","filters"],"repository":{"type":"git","url":"git+https://github.com/iamvdo/pleeease-filters.git"},"scripts":{"test":"jasmine-node spec"},"dependencies":{"onecolor":"~2.4.0","postcss":"^5.0.4"},"devDependencies":{"jasmine-node":"~1.14.3"},"gitHead":"8fc51b30738058a619279a5931632a34dd6e462e","bugs":{"url":"https://github.com/iamvdo/pleeease-filters/issues"},"homepage":"https://github.com/iamvdo/pleeease-filters#readme","_id":"pleeease-filters@3.0.0","_shasum":"35a4d4c2086413eabc2ce17aaa2ec29054e3075c","_from":".","_npmVersion":"2.14.4","_nodeVersion":"4.1.2","_npmUser":{"name":"iamvdo","email":"vincent@iamvdo.me"},"maintainers":[{"name":"iamvdo","email":"vincent@iamvdo.me"}],"dist":{"shasum":"35a4d4c2086413eabc2ce17aaa2ec29054e3075c","tarball":"https://registry.npmjs.org/pleeease-filters/-/pleeease-filters-3.0.0.tgz"},"_npmOperationalInternal":{"host":"packages-12-west.internal.npmjs.com","tmp":"tmp/pleeease-filters-3.0.0.tgz_1459498419986_0.007074285764247179"},"directories":{}},"3.0.1":{"name":"pleeease-filters","version":"3.0.1","description":"Convert CSS shorthand filters to SVG ones","author":{"name":"Vincent De Oliveira"},"main":"./index","keywords":["postprocessor","css","postcss","pleeease","filters"],"repository":{"type":"git","url":"git+https://github.com/iamvdo/pleeease-filters.git"},"scripts":{"test":"jasmine-node spec"},"dependencies":{"onecolor":"~2.4.0","postcss":"^5.0.4"},"devDependencies":{"jasmine-node":"~1.14.3"},"gitHead":"ee94bbb011363cf1f61343255f077a789418a984","bugs":{"url":"https://github.com/iamvdo/pleeease-filters/issues"},"homepage":"https://github.com/iamvdo/pleeease-filters#readme","_id":"pleeease-filters@3.0.1","_shasum":"4dfe0e8f1046613517c64b728bc80608a7ebf22f","_from":".","_npmVersion":"3.10.10","_nodeVersion":"6.9.4","_npmUser":{"name":"iamvdo","email":"vincent@iamvdo.me"},"maintainers":[{"name":"iamvdo","email":"vincent@iamvdo.me"}],"dist":{"shasum":"4dfe0e8f1046613517c64b728bc80608a7ebf22f","tarball":"https://registry.npmjs.org/pleeease-filters/-/pleeease-filters-3.0.1.tgz"},"_npmOperationalInternal":{"host":"packages-12-west.internal.npmjs.com","tmp":"tmp/pleeease-filters-3.0.1.tgz_1486486320554_0.21615364542230964"},"directories":{}},"4.0.0":{"name":"pleeease-filters","version":"4.0.0","description":"Convert CSS shorthand filters to SVG ones","author":{"name":"Vincent De Oliveira"},"main":"./index","keywords":["postprocessor","css","postcss","pleeease","filters"],"repository":{"type":"git","url":"git+https://github.com/iamvdo/pleeease-filters.git"},"scripts":{"test":"jasmine-node spec"},"dependencies":{"onecolor":"^3.0.4","postcss":"^6.0.1"},"devDependencies":{"jasmine-node":"~1.14.3"},"gitHead":"2f09086f8be1343016b058370ae7222238513492","bugs":{"url":"https://github.com/iamvdo/pleeease-filters/issues"},"homepage":"https://github.com/iamvdo/pleeease-filters#readme","_id":"pleeease-filters@4.0.0","_shasum":"6632b2fb05648d2758d865384fbced79e1ccaec7","_from":".","_npmVersion":"4.4.1","_nodeVersion":"7.7.3","_npmUser":{"name":"iamvdo","email":"vincent@iamvdo.me"},"maintainers":[{"name":"iamvdo","email":"vincent@iamvdo.me"}],"dist":{"shasum":"6632b2fb05648d2758d865384fbced79e1ccaec7","tarball":"https://registry.npmjs.org/pleeease-filters/-/pleeease-filters-4.0.0.tgz"},"_npmOperationalInternal":{"host":"packages-12-west.internal.npmjs.com","tmp":"tmp/pleeease-filters-4.0.0.tgz_1494332162841_0.6904598891269416"},"directories":{}}},"readme":"Pleeease: filters\r\n=================\r\n\r\nConvert CSS shorthand filters to SVG equivalent.\r\n\r\nUsed by [Pleeease](https://github.com/iamvdo/pleeease), a CSS post-processor.\r\n\r\nTry it by yourself in the [Pleeease playground](http://pleeease.io/playground.html?div%20%7B%0A%20%20filter:%20blur(4px)%0A%7D)\r\n\r\n##Example\r\n\r\nYou write `foo.css`:\r\n\r\n```css\r\n.blur {\r\n\tfilter: blur(4px);\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nYou get `bar.css`:\r\n\r\n```css\r\n.blur {\r\n\tfilter: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><filter id=\"filter\"><feGaussianBlur stdDeviation=\"4\" /></filter></svg>#filter');\r\n\tfilter: blur(4px);\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n##Filters\r\n\r\nIt converts all 10 CSS shorthand filters:\r\n\r\n* grayscale\r\n* sepia\r\n* saturate\r\n* hue-rotate\r\n* invert\r\n* opacity\r\n* brightness\r\n* contrast\r\n* blur\r\n* drop-shadow\r\n\r\nLearn [more about CSS filters](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/filter)\r\n\r\n##Prefixes\r\n\r\nThis tool doesn't add prefixes. If you want them, you should use [Autoprefixer](https://github.com/ai/autoprefixer). This is what [Pleeease](https://github.com/iamvdo/pleeease) does:\r\n\r\n```css\r\n.blur {\r\n\tfilter: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><filter id=\"filter\"><feGaussianBlur stdDeviation=\"4\" /></filter></svg>#filter');\r\n\t-webkit-filter: blur(4px);\r\n\t        filter: blur(4px);\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n##Usage\r\n\r\n\t$ npm install pleeease-filters\r\n\r\n```javascript\r\nvar filters = require('pleeease-filters'),\r\n\tfs      = require('fs');\r\n\r\nvar css = fs.readFileSync('app.css', 'utf8');\r\n\r\n// define options here\r\nvar options = {};\r\n\r\nvar fixed = filters.process(css, options);\r\n\r\nfs.writeFile('app.min.css', fixed, function (err) {\r\n  if (err) {\r\n    throw err;\r\n  }\r\n  console.log('File saved!');\r\n});\r\n```\r\n##Options\r\n\r\nYou can also add IE filters with an option:\r\n\r\n```javascript\r\n// set options\r\nvar options = {\r\n\toldIE: true\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nUsing the first example, you'll get:\r\n\r\n```css\r\n.blur {\r\n\tfilter: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><filter id=\"filter\"><feGaussianBlur stdDeviation=\"4\" /></filter></svg>#filter');\r\n\tfilter: blur(4px);\r\n\tfilter: progid:DXImageTransform.Microsoft.Blur(pixelradius=4);\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n##Note\r\n\r\n**Be careful**, not all browsers support CSS or SVG filters on HTML content:\r\n\r\n* latest WebKit browsers support CSS shorthand\r\n* Firefox support SVG filters (and CSS shorthand since FF35)\r\n* IE9- support IE filters (limited and slightly degraded)\r\n\r\n**It means that IE10+, Opera Mini and Android browsers have no support at all on HTML, only in SVG.**\r\n\r\nMoreover, IE filters shouldn't be used.\r\n\r\nSee [caniuse](http://caniuse.com/#feat=svg-filters) for more info.\r\n\r\n##Licence\r\n\r\nMIT Â© 2014 [Vincent De Oliveira &middot; iamvdo](https://github.com/iamvdo)\r\n\r\nThis module is an adaptation of [CSS-Filters-Polyfill](https://github.com/Schepp/CSS-Filters-Polyfill). Copyright (c) 2012 - 2013 Christian Schepp Schaefer\r\n","maintainers":[{"name":"iamvdo","email":"vincent@iamvdo.me"}],"time":{"modified":"2018-02-09T19:31:50.429Z","created":"2014-07-02T12:01:14.880Z","0.1.0":"2014-07-02T12:01:16.570Z","0.1.1":"2014-07-02T20:44:59.665Z","0.1.2":"2014-07-02T20:59:45.012Z","0.1.3":"2014-07-07T13:51:50.763Z","0.1.4":"2014-12-11T10:10:42.860Z","0.1.5":"2014-12-23T10:46:48.087Z","1.0.0":"2015-01-27T11:05:59.749Z","1.0.1":"2015-05-25T16:00:10.215Z","2.0.0":"2015-09-14T08:47:00.521Z","3.0.0":"2016-04-01T08:13:42.472Z","3.0.1":"2017-02-07T16:52:02.276Z","4.0.0":"2017-05-09T12:16:04.708Z"},"readmeFilename":"README.md","keywords":["postprocessor","css","postcss","pleeease","filters"],"author":{"name":"Vincent De Oliveira"},"repository":{"type":"git","url":"git+https://github.com/iamvdo/pleeease-filters.git"},"bugs":{"url":"https://github.com/iamvdo/pleeease-filters/issues"},"homepage":"https://github.com/iamvdo/pleeease-filters#readme","users":{"ramiroespada":true},"_attachments":{},"_etag":"W/\"37c09bb2776caeb2a1fe6fd2cff6eada\"","_lastModified":"Sun, 27 May 2018 12:24:45 GMT","_cached":true}